beers.description: The No. 1 selling Belgian beer worldwide, Stella Artois has a rich heritage dating back to 1366 in Leuven, Belgium, and is today the gold-standard of quality in over 80 countries. The art and science of enjoying Stella Artois extends from the finest ingredients, to the exacting 9-step Pouring Ritual, to the specially crafted chalice in which it is best served. - See more at: http://tapintoyourbeer.com/index.cfm?id=423#sthash.iiYMDvbG.dpuf
